{{Infobox oil refinery | name = Come By Chance Refinery | image = | caption = | country = [[Canada]] | province = [[Newfoundland and Labrador]] | city = [[Come By Chance, Newfoundland and Labrador|Come By Chance]] | location_map = Canada Newfoundland and Labrador | location_map_text = Location of Come By Chance Refinery in Newfoundland and Labrador | coordinates = {{coord|47|47|57|N|53|59|45|W|type:landmark_region:CA|display=inline,title}} | operator = [[North Atlantic Refining]] | owner = [[North Atlantic Refining]] | parent = | founded = 1973 | closure = | capacity = | capacity bbl/d = 130,000 | employees = 400 | ref units = [[alkylation]], [[isomerisation]], [[distillation]] of crude oil, [[hydrocracking]], reforming catalytic, cracking catalytic, [[desulphuration]] | oil tank = 50 | oil refining center = }}
'''Come By Chance Refinery''' (also known as '''North Atlantic Refinery''') is a crude oil refinery located in [[Come By Chance, Newfoundland and Labrador|Come By Chance]] in [[Newfoundland and Labrador]], [[Canada]]. It has a refinery capacity of {{convert|130000|oilbbl/d}}. It is operated by [[North Atlantic Refining]] and was owned by [[Korea National Oil Corporation]] until 2014, when SilverRange Capital Partners, a New-York Based commodity merchant bank, bought the refinery. SilverRange is now Silverpeak Strategic Partners.
==History== The refinery was built by [[John Shaheen]]'s Shaheen Resources in 1971–1973. It was operated in 1973–1976 until the bankruptcy of Shaheen Resources. The refinery was restarted in 1986 by Newfoundland Processing Ltd. In August 1994, the [[Vitol|Vitol Group]] purchased the refinery and the operating company North Atlantic Refining was founded. In October 2006, [[Calgary]]-based [[Harvest Energy Trust]] purchased North Atlantic Refining for $1.6&nbsp;billion, and in October 2009, the company was purchased by [[Korea National Oil Corporation]]. The refinery was expanded to a capacity of 130,000 bbl after a revamp by Silverpeak in 2016. <ref name=history>{{cite web |title = History of the Refinery at Come by Chance |publisher = [[North Atlantic Refining]] |url = http://www.narefining.ca/history.asp |accessdate = 2010-01-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160611190010/http://www.narefining.ca/history.asp |archive-date = 2016-06-11 |dead-url = yes |df = }}</ref>
