'''Roma Plastilina''' is a brand of non-hardening [[Modelling clay|modeling clay]] sold by Spanish company JOVI and its subsidiaries.  JOVI Modeling Clay, Plastilina, is mainly composed of [[Biomass|vegetable matter]], making it lighter and giving 33% more volume. It is sold on the internet and in many arts and craft stores.{{citation needed|date=August 2010}}.

